<p>I originally posted some of this data <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/forum/t-11130369/all-k-class-scenarios-used-in-scps">in the forums</a> after a few days procrastinating at work, manually pulling things from k-class-scenario tagges articles. I thought I would make it pretty.</p>
<p>Also, please, anyone, have at!</p>
